[codex] - Both passes converge on the three-paragraph structure (current state ΓåÆ countervailing patterns ΓåÆ theoretical sharpening) verbatim.
[codex] - The two `FORMAT TBD` entries that remain (Marketplace 2026 on Nationwide/UPS rebranding; Paradigm 2025 Fortune 100 report) should be vetted by JC before submission.
